    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constellum is a multiplayer card-driven tactics game with accessibility at its heart.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/626cf0fa1e971bc00ba82a3e017eb54a.poster.avif?t=1769402301\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/626cf0fa1e971bc00ba82a3e017eb54a.webm?t=1769402301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/626cf0fa1e971bc00ba82a3e017eb54a.mp4?t=1769402301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Constelleum, the team vs team cosmic fantasy card battler. Pick from characters with distinct styles and mechanics. Play cards to move, disrupt opponents, summon companions, and more. Coordinate with your teammates to drive points to the opposing goal and claim victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/6396dced086b48a84e38573f0a7e11ce.poster.avif?t=1769402301\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/6396dced086b48a84e38573f0a7e11ce.webm?t=1769402301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/6396dced086b48a84e38573f0a7e11ce.mp4?t=1769402301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We made Constelleum accessible from design through development</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Constelleum integrates <strong>turn-based tactics</strong> (think Gloomhaven), the <strong>asymmetric characters</strong> of MOBAs, and <strong>deck building</strong> into a low-input and competitive experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize against another team in <strong>online versus multiplayer</strong> for deep, emergent gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join friends in a <strong>cooperative roguelite</strong> to outwit encounters, forge a path, and explore the World Beasts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work together to perform <strong>exciting combos</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/09093257da2089e559023c1b379b4251.poster.avif?t=1769402301\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/09093257da2089e559023c1b379b4251.webm?t=1769402301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796970/extras/09093257da2089e559023c1b379b4251.mp4?t=1769402301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 playable characters with their own mechanics and resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expansive card libraries unique to each character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative mechanics offer a rich new way to build decks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple immersive World Beasts to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens of status effects</p></li></ul>",
